        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="product-card">

      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1516321318423-f06f85e504b3?q=80&w=1400&auto=format&fit=crop">

      <div class="product-content">
        <h3>Metal PCB</h3>
