      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="application-card">

      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504384308090-c894fdcc538d?q=80&w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop">

      <div class="application-content">
        <h3>통신 산업</h3>

